{
  "stem": "1641.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- the conditions in-- Mauthausen was flooded by all the other camps got evacuated, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the whole of Auschwitz was pumped into Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the camps around Vienna was pushed into Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So a barrack built for 200 people was housing 1,200.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was six people to a-- to a bed-- not bed, but a piece of timber, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Six people, six here, six there, six under the beds, six between the beds, and what did the commander do?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They pushed 1,200 people in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had to put people into the corridors, between the beds, and the road leading to the so-called toilet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The toilet was just a dug hole in the ground, at the end of the building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was one meter deep, filled with excreta, and urine, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so even the road to there was filled with people, lying on top of each other, like wedged in a-- you know, 1,200 people-- better than being outside in the snow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I got my place inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was-- people couldn't sleep, they were so tightly packed, legs everywhere in your face.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Half the people had high temperature-- you know, for-- from the Auschwitz people, you know, coming in the open wagon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was really very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was half unconscious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had high temperature by that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had soup again next day, had a tiny piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then they started to call out numbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We got our number, your numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they called out numbers to different works, mostly in tunnels, because Austria was full with tunnels by then, where all the German were manufacturing industries, plus the rockets.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all built inside the tunnels, because the tunnels the Americans couldn't bomb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the mountain.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
